narrator: I open the closet. Just some old coats, my bowler cap, back when I was a bachelor and thought it fashionable and— what’s this?
narrator: A cloak and cowl, black just like the killers. Yes, I remember! It was from an old Dracula Costume, from years ago.
narrator: How strange… does that mean the killer broke into our home first? Perhaps expected to see Elonai alone? I don’t know, but best take this cloak as evidence.
